[url=https://flic.kr/p/zSx4C4][img]https://farm1.staticflickr.com/697/22231658799_3aa37cfc61_c.jpg[/img][/url]

Hello everyone
Sorry for my bad english it's not my first language
well, i make this ENB based on the 0.279 enb. you can download it [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0279.htm]here[/url]

My pc config: intel core 2 duo e8400 3.00 Ghz
                    x2 amd radeon hd 4000 1Go
                    3 Gb of RAM


I run it with 40 fps, so no need NASA pc
Crossfire are able to run the DOF 

I let The screenshots spoke by themself 
Don't froget to report me if you have some bugs 

[color=#cc0000][size=5]Config needed:[/size][/color]
 
This ENB don't need a high end 

minimal config:
Processor: Dual core 2.5 GHZ
Graphic card: 1gb 
Ram: 3 gb
[color=#cc0000][size=5]How to install:[/size][/color]
[size=2]You must place all files in the main folder C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim[/size]

Put in skyrimpref.ini : bTreesReceiveShadows=1
                                 bDrawLandShadows=1
                                 bShadowsOnGrass=1

To find it: C:\ User\ [username]\ Documents\ My games\ Skyrim\ Skyrimprefs.ini
